CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 7, 1955, pg. 12, reads: "Contest Winners - The lucky winners in popularity contest, sponsored by the Beauty Shop Owners and the Pennsylvania State Cosmetologists, are shown here with Earsley Kincaid who presented prizes. Left to right, third winner, Yvonne Kershaw, who won a trip to Washington, D. C., Mrs. Kincaid, first prize winner of the trip to Bermuda, Dorothy Matthews, and second winner Dorothy Morton, who won a trip to New York. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, including Earsley Kincaid presenting prizes to Yvonne Kershaw, Dorothy Matthews, and Dorothy Morton, in Fort Pitt Hotel for Pittsburgh Beauty Shop Owners and Pennsylvania State Cosmetologists conference
